column12:
'desc': [u'

Nuby Natural Touch Breast Express Breast Pump Set - Manual Price: Rs.775

Nursing mothers often have to deal with engorgement which can be painful and rather inconvenient
column13: especially if you are travelling. But Nuby presents a discreet solution that can help new mothers express breast milk instantly and pain-free. The Nuby On-the-go Breast Pump is a manual breast pump that is easy to use and has been designed to make expressing more comfortable and convenient. The On-the-Go Breast Pump has a compact design
column14:
making it perfect for travel.

\r\n

\r\n\tThe breast pump comes with a 90 ml silicone storage container with a sealing cap that allows you to collect the expressed breast milk. The 100 per cent BPA free Nuby Manual Breast pump offers a safe
column15: comfortable and hygienic way to express and store breast milk
column16:
making the life of a new mother much easier.

\xa0
